  "prompt": "How much do CATIA Specialist level certification exams cost?",
  "response": "The cost of CATIA Specialist level certification exams can vary based on location, the certification provider, and any associated training costs. Typically, the exam fees can range from a few hundred to over a thousand dollars. It's best to check with the official certification provider or authorized training centers for the most accurate and up-to-date pricing. Additionally, there may be discounts for students or bulk purchases if you're part of a training program.",
